Alvis-Convert version 0.3
================================

This is a module collecting Alvis XML format conversion methods for any 
number of source formats.

Contains these conversion scripts:

    alvis_wikipedia_add_cats.pl
    news_xml2alvis.pl
    wikipedia2alvis.pl
    html2alvis.pl
    html2plain.pl
    ainodump2alvis.pl
    alvisDecollect.pl
    alvisXMLmerge.pl
    alvisXMLsplit.pl
    alvisXMLjoin.pl
    alvisXSL.pl
    alvisSource.pl

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Data::Dumper
   Storable
   Encode
   Encode::Guess
   XML::LibXML
   Compress::Zlib
   HTML::Encoding
   File::Type
   File::Find
   Parse::MediaWikiDump
   Digest::MD5
   MIME::Base64
   Time::Simple
   Carp
   Cwd

Additionally, the scripts in bin/ require:

   File::Copy
   File::Path
   Getopt::Long
   IO::Handle
   Pod::Usage
   POSIX
   Time::HiRes
   Alvis::Pipeline

